
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UPPERCASE Conventional Commits — Content Workspace
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Format:
#   TYPE(scope): description
#
#   [optional body]
#
#   [optional footer(s)]
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TYPE (required, UPPERCASE) — pick one:
#
#   CONTENT   New or updated vault content (notes, pages)
#   DOCS      Changes to documentation or guides
#   FIX       Corrections to existing content (typos, broken links)
#   REFACTOR  Reorganization without changing meaning (moves, renames)
#   CHORE     Maintenance (templates, folder org, vault config)
#   META      Changes to vault infrastructure (.obsidian, .claude, .gitignore)
#   STYLE     Formatting changes only (no content change)
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SCOPE (optional) — area of vault affected:
#   e.g., (inbox), (templates), (archive), (config), (metadata), (skills)
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BODY (optional) — explain what and why, not how.
#   Separate from description with a blank line.
#
# FOOTER (optional) — references:
#   e.g., Closes #42
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
